de. Suspecting that a robot may be responsible for the death, his investigation leads him to believe that humanity may be in danger.","genre_ids":[28,878],"popularity":7.874,"vote_count":12455,"poster_path":"/efwv6F2lGaghjPpBRSINHtoEiZB.jpg","release_date":"2004-07-15","vote_average":6.959,"backdrop_path":"/lOXVbF2mBK0xUt8sLInF3TIk5YS.jpg","original_title":"I, Robot","original_language":"en"},{"id":766423,"adult":false,"title":"Puparia","video":false,"overview":"Something is about to change drastically, and the only thing to do is to witness it.","genre_ids":[16,18,14],"popularity":0.1282,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/3KRpbwNDrQ8cqKoVknoPqqtrpAO.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-23","vote_average":7.958,"backdrop_path":"/6HRvFDiP894qvRLMu0nM0WeNbiC.jpg","original_title":"Puparia","original_language":"ja"},{"id":420544,"adult":false,"title":"Cheerfu11y","video":false,"overview":"Cheerfu11y (Cheerfu11y チアフリー) is a 2011 Japanese cheerleading film directed by Shō Tsukikawa.  The movie served as Universal Music Japan's second movie in the Japanese movie market, following the success of its first offering, the action film \"Run 60\".  This cheerleading movie starring 11 idols called, 'Cheerfu11y'. The movie stars Kikkawa Yuu and ex-Momoiro Clover member Hayami Akari. Alongside them are Passpo☆ members Tamai Anna, Anzai Naomi, Sakuma Kaho, and Mori Shiori. 'Up-Up Girls' Furukawa Kontasu and Mori Saki will join them, along with Akiyama Yurika and Goto Yuki from 'THE Possible', and Niwa Mikiho from 'Canary Club'.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.1576,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/yQcLhIySsh1P0Qx9jc9YtpU92v8.jpg","release_date":"2011-10-22","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/nUk7IjHam80XXgrWKRsdS4FS4YD.jpg","original_title":"Cheerfu11y","original_language":"ja"},{"id":949394,"adult":false,"title":"Ensemble Stars!! -Road to Show--","video":false,"overview":"Ensemble Square - a brand new building in the middle of the city where countless people come and go. It’s home to four offices belonging to idols who spend their days singing and dancing. Films starring the Ensemble Square idols have been nominated for the Idol Film Festival (IFF), an annual festival held in New York City, and representative idols are selected to attend. The boys jet off to NYC to attend the festival and reception party, and afterward, head out on the town to see the sights and sounds. But a suspicious shadow is creeping up on them…","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.7096,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/hW4Y4Fy8khf4D3tlvwV82txg1uy.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/eTfbiJANxSTnrISIL9JSGeI8uur.jpg","original_title":"あんさんぶるスターズ！！-Road to Show!!-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":591802,"adult":false,"title":"Reol Japan Tour 2018 - MADE IN FACTION","video":true,"overview":"Reol live on stage during her Japan Tour in Tokyo 2018","genre_ids":[10402],"popularity":0.2018,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/aVWvHyXuKwjTeiAk0PevnOVtKQH.jpg","release_date":"2019-03-20","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/dkhoR8Fd4m4LMDGFop49xjSUmCW.jpg","original_title":"Reol Japan Tour 2018 - MADE IN FACTION","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt33050528","twitter_id":"pj_sekai","facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q128041782","instagram_id":null,"rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/colorful_stage_the_movie_a_miku_who_cant_sing"},"social_ids":{"twitter":"pj_sekai","facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":101790,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":["Sensitive Themes"],"release_date":"2025-06-05T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"10"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","rel